<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>WeatherApp</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/weather.css" />
    <script src="/js/weather.js"></script>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body background="/images/weather.png">
    <div>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <a class="navbar-brand welcome" href="#">
            <img
              src="/images/weather.png"
              alt=""
              width="30"
              height="24"
              class="d-inline-block align-text-top"
            />
            Welcome..!!</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <div class="weather-desc">
        Do you excited to get current weather report of any city in the world..?
        Then why you are waiting, type the city you want to know about weather
        and know about it..!!
      </div>

      <div style="margin-left: 32vw;">
        <input
          class="form-control me-2"
          type="search"
          id="weather-city-search"
          placeholder="Search"
          aria-label="Search"
          onkeyup="hideWeatherInfoBlock()"
        />
        <button
          class="btn btn-outline-success search-button"
          onclick="getTheWeatherData()"
        >Search</button>
      </div>
      <div id="weather-main">
        <p id="weather-info"></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>